data.description: Spacious two story home. Offers both casual and formal dining areas as well as a family and living room.  Also, an oversized Master with en suite and walk in closet.  Bonus/Game room upstairs, a second story screened in balcony the length of the house overlooking the pool and Eagle Dunes Golf course. Updates include (10/2023) Roof, AC unit, Water heater and more. Minutes away from down town Mount Dora's parks lakes, dining and shopping. Also, easy access to SR 429.
